class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Domain\\Event\\CoreLifecycleEventType"
type: final class
summary: CoreLifecycleEventType provides static utility methods for identifying and validating core lifecycle event types within the agent domain. It serves as a central registry for mapping event types to their corresponding class implementations and enforcing ordering constraints.
